Why ooes we use require function?
where does the require function comes in pictures?
we can load three kinds of modules in nodejs
1).Core module('http')
2).Developer module('./lib/controller')
3)3rd party module from npm('express')
here the node automatically finds the core modules load it 
the developers module starts with a '.'

each module having the private function is crucial

we use module.export to export a function


